Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.49,0:23:39.68,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(120,120)}會遇到些許挫折
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.99,0:23:43.57,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(120,120)}即使萬事俱備
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.89,0:23:46.79,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(120,120)}也需要有人來引導
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.91,0:23:49.46,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(120,120)}現在最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.64,0:23:52.89,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(120,120)}害怕再次放手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.13,0:23:58.49,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(120,120)}但是我所期待的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.61,0:24:01.77,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(120,120)}盡在此處
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.95,0:24:06.98,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(120,120)}盡在此處
